  <scopecontent id="aspace_1008b428e0b35650e8667aee0d4342aa">
    <head>Scope and Content note</head>
<p>The <emph render="italic">Signal</emph> Archive contains correspondence and manuscripts submitted to the journal's editor, Bret Rohmer.  Notable authors of manuscript submissions include Hart Crane, Diane Di Prima, Kirby Doyle, LeRoi Jones, Ron Loewinsohn, David Meltzer, W.S. Merwin, Frank O'Hara, Joel Oppenheimer, Michael Rumaker, John Thomas, John Wieners, and Paul Zweig.</p>  </scopecontent>
